{"arkId":"cl010093009","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010093009","modified ":"2026-01-19","title":"Pi\u00e9destal d\u00e9cor\u00e9 de quatre figures de proph\u00e8tes, sous des arcatures","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Pi\u00e9destal d\u00e9cor\u00e9 de quatre figures de proph\u00e8tes, sous des arcatures"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1267 - 1300","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1267,"endYear":1300,"imprecision":"","text":"3e tiers du XIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"France \u00cele-de-France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 478","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"pi\u00e9destal","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"\u0152uvre restaur\u00e9e et \u00e9l\u00e9ments pr\u00e9par\u00e9s en vue d\u0027une restauration (t\u00eates)","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1,25","displayDimension":"1,25 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0,415","displayDimension":"0,415 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,595","displayDimension":"0,595 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"pierre calcaire","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"porte des Valois (France-\u003ESaint-Denis-\u003Eabbaye-\u003E\u00e9glise)","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Partie basse du trumeau de la porte des Valois, ouverte au croisillon nord du transept de l\u0027abbaye b\u00e9n\u00e9dictine de Saint-Denis. Supportait une statue de la Vierge tenant l\u0027Enfant, disparue, mais dont la t\u00eate, est, peut-\u00eatre, conserv\u00e9e au Louvre (RF 450). Abbaye devenue bien national \u00e0 la R\u00e9volution. Eglise affect\u00e9e au culte paroissial, saccag\u00e9e en ao\u00fbt 1793, utilis\u00e9e comme Temple de la Raison de novembre 1793 \u00e0 avril 1794, laiss\u00e9e ensuite \u00e0 l\u0027abandon. Portail mutil\u00e9. Statues des \u00e9brasements et plusieurs t\u00eates des voussures recueillies au mus\u00e9e des Monuments fran\u00e7ais. Trumeau d\u00e9pos\u00e9 et utilis\u00e9 pour l\u0027ex\u00e9cution de la copie plac\u00e9e in situ lors des travaux de restauration ex\u00e9cut\u00e9s en 1871 par le sculpteur Louis Villeminot sous les ordres d\u0027Eug\u00e8ne Viollet-le-Duc. Magasins de Saint-Denis. Versement des Chantiers de Saint-Denis,1881 (arr\u00eat\u00e9 du 28 juillet 1881)","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"versement","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"28\/07\/1881","startYear":1881,"endYear":1881}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"versement"}],"material":[{"value":"pierre calcaire"}],"place":[{"value":"porte des Valois"}],"objectType":[{"value":"pi\u00e9destal"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Le Pogam, Pierre-Yves, \u00ab Un art du recyclage : des sculptures gothiques remploy\u00e9es dans des fa\u00e7ades gothiques \u00bb, Cahiers arch\u00e9ologiques, t. 56, 2015, p. 149-172","bibliographyDate":"2015","bibliographyDetail":"p. 156, note 32","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Le Pog